The paper focuses on Question Answering (QA) and discusses algorithmic components and data augmentation strategies that have yielded state-of-the-art results on benchmark datasets like SQuAD. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of Natural Language Processing (NLP) (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper evaluates on the Natural Questions benchmark dataset, which is a large-scale QA dataset, indicating that it could also belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
